==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Undeniable
<hw>Undeniable</hw>  <def>See <er>deniable</er>.</def>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Undeniable
<hw>Un`de*ni"a*ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Not
deniable; incapable of denial; palpably true; indisputable; obvious;
<as>as, <ex>undeniable</ex> evidence</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Unobjectionable; unquestionably excellent; <as>as, a
person of <ex>undeniable</ex> connections</as>.</def>
<mark>[Colloq.]</mark> <rj><au>G. Eliot.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Undeniably</ent>⟦br⟧
